00:02:58,840 --> 00:03:01,880
So this is obviously a Catholic church.

67
00:03:01,880 --> 00:03:07,780
Catholicism here is radically different from what Americans think of Catholicism.

68
00:03:07,820 --> 00:03:12,700
In America, there's a lot of emphasis on sin and living a moral lifestyle.

69
00:03:12,700 --> 00:03:15,860
Here, it's less of that. A lot of people here

70
00:03:15,860 --> 00:03:17,720
seem to have the attitude that

71
00:03:17,720 --> 00:03:19,560
you can do whatever you want during the week,

72
00:03:19,560 --> 00:03:22,200
but so long as you tell Jesus you love him,

73
00:03:22,200 --> 00:03:23,420
He'll forgive you.

74
00:03:23,420 --> 00:03:27,560
There's a lot of influence from the native religions before Catholicism.

75
00:03:27,560 --> 00:03:33,240
So animism has a lot of influence. A lot of influence from animism.

76
00:03:33,240 --> 00:03:34,700
And other native things.

77
00:03:34,700 --> 00:03:38,260
So you'll see people going to church,

78
00:03:38,260 --> 00:03:41,800
lighting candles for sculptures and pictures,

79
00:03:41,800 --> 00:03:46,520
touching pictures of saints or the Virgin Mary,

80
00:03:46,520 --> 00:03:48,400
crying and stuff...

81
00:03:48,400 --> 00:03:51,220
When you see that, it's a little hard to imagine

82
00:03:51,220 --> 00:03:54,220
Americans doing something like that and being so dramatic.

83
