107
00:05:17,600 --> 00:05:20,100
in terms of the food they eat here,

108
00:05:20,100 --> 00:05:22,380
the holidays,

109
00:05:22,380 --> 00:05:25,780
and Chinese people are very superstitious -

110
00:05:25,820 --> 00:05:27,980
Filipinos very superstitious,

111
00:05:27,980 --> 00:05:30,860
so there's a lot of crossover in terms of all of that.

